responses.title: Who said you could stroll in my woods?
Watch your step, eh? Heaps of danger about.
There's no end to the things I can do to you.
Throw down your gold, I might let you live.
Say hello to my little friend.
Don't even think about it, I can drop the lot of you before you can spit.
Let's not get squirrely now, it'd be a shame to have to kill you.
I'm sorry, did you think you were hunting me?
Where do you think you're going?
Who said you could stroll in my woods?
And don't think I'll run out of ammo. I've always got another stash.
Drop your gold and run along then.
Cross me and I'll cross you out.
The wood teaches one rule: step fast or you're snack meat.
I'm mean as, and twice as quick!
I step through the forest like it's not even there.
Everything's a bit of a game if you ask me!
You ever hear the one about the tortoise and the hare and the squirrel that shot 'em both?
Touch my rig and you lose a finger.
Hey, hold this target for a sec.
Better not catch you littering, bro!
Watch your step, eh? Heaps of danger about.
Don't even think about it, I can drop the lot of you before you can spit.
Let's not get squirrely now, it'd be a shame to have to kill you.
Maybe I'll get straight to the point.
What's this then, some kind of fight?
What's this, amateur hour? I'll hand out a few pointers.
Hey, side bets on the body count?
Oh wow! I've never seen so many interesting people to kill in one place! I'm sure heaps'll be friendly too.
Cross me and I'll cross you out.
The wood teaches one rule: step fast or you're snack meat.
I'm mean as, and twice as quick.
I step through the forest like it's not even there.
Better watch where you're going, never know what's lurking in the deep wood.
Ehhh, there's some nice woodland around here. Guess I could be bothered.
I'm not for hire... But this does pique my interest.
Everything's a bit of a game if you ask me!
Fair's for you to worry about.
Gonna stand here all day, or sniff out a bit of fun?
If you've heard of me, I must be doing something wrong...
What do I look like, a hunter? I'm a vegetarian... most of the time.
My aims are my own, best you don't end up as one of them.
Civilization always looked an awful lot like a boot heel.
Criminals are the ones obsessed with fire, so what if I burned some of their stuff?
I've been dodging Durana Beasts since before I could crawl. What's this lot gonna do to me?
All them idiots can keep the big smoke. Out here's where a body is really free!
No worries really only applies to me. That bunch should have heaps of worry.
You ever hear the one about the tortoise and the hare and the squirrel that shot them both?
Every time you hear a twig snap, that's me about to end your run.
I was born with nothing to lose. There's nothing they can do to stop me.
Why would I name it? It just a piece of wood. A really awesome piece of wood, but still.
Let's chase down a few bolt holes.
Surviving adolescence was a harder fight than this.
Touch my rig and you'll lose a finger.
You want a bag? I can get you a bag. What kind of bag?
I don't care what's in the bag. I just know I'm not about to let the other lot have it.

There's a lot of more we could do with a bag if you ask me. Which no one ever does. Because why on earth would they? We're not exactly talking about geniuses are we? Honestly, there's a real lack of imagination around here.
I don't see what all the fuss is about. For me the battle never stops.
So we keeping score now? Gotcha.
I don't know the rules, but I'll learn along the way.
They say whoever wins this fight will get to call all the shots, but me, I don't want anybody calling the shots.
There's something hauntingly familiar about all this.
Step fast and shoot straight. It's gonna be a hell of a fight.
Did you see a branch move?
I'm always on the right trail.
Always wanted to go this way.
I'm keen, not literally of course.
Nah yeah, I know I know.
Nah yeah, I know I know.
Lets do this the easy way.
How do you like my rig?
Where do you think you're going?
Drop your gold and run along then.
Are you gonna be a problem?
Hey you wanna see something really cool?
Hey, hold this target for a sec.
Do us a favor and stand real still.
It's why you came, isn't it?
Claw em' to death if I have to.
This is gourmet cooking around here.
Spruce the place up a bit.
We can make a little fort.
Hey, how ya going in there?
Get a bit caught up then?
It's more for fun than sport.
Always always always watch where you're walking.
You look all sorts of wrong.
Caught ya in your stubbies did we?
Ever seen someone bleed out in a net? No? Let's get started.
I usually like my trees to myself, but I'll make an exception.
It's not even my birthday. Oh, I guess it could be...
Wanna see what we do for fun around here?
For the record, I did hit the tree.
Good news! I've decided how I'm gonna kill you!
Sure, wind me up. Great idea.
Right. So it's the hard way.
Chin up. This'll only hurt quite a bit.
I can take the kick. Can you?
It's funny, cause it's really unwinding for me.
I can't believe you just stood there!
Now you gotta work for it.
Not my fault they don't duck.
I don't relish hurting folks. But it can be funny. And sometimes I do relish it a bit.
Blows you back a bit eh?
This is why I get outta bed in the morning.
Can't hit nothing if you don't pull the trigger.
We can make a little fort!
I'll just cozy up with this one.
Am I here and there...or neither here nor there?
Who doesn't love the swirly bits?
Better not end up anywhere suss.
I'm not sure this isn't killing me!
Good thing there's not a blood price.
It's definitely one way to travel.
Hope it's not a one-way ticket.
Another one of these bloody things?
Who even keeps these up? I should boost 'em.
There's some abandoned ones of these round where I grew up. Fun to play in.
I don't want it. But they sure as heck aren't getting it.
Wait, we're not burning it? I already got the pine pitch...
Whose stupid idea was it to put these things here anyway?
It doesn't hurt the other side's proper thick.
It's almost like divine intervention. If I believed in that sorta stuff. Which I do not.
That all went straight to the tail.
Just cuz I'm never gonna grow old doesn't mean I don't wanna level up.
Makes me feel all warm and fuzzy.
There's good, there's better, and then there's plain old me.
Don't any of you ever get tired of congratulating yourselves?
Yeah yeah, don't get a big head.
Everything just got a little bit keener.
I'll punch a Durana right in its stupid eye and take a tentacle for snarlers!
Oh sweet. Wanna see something really cool? We'll need a handy target.
I didn't get this good NOT to kill stuff.
My oh my. Now's when we get to the good stuff.
OK, so this is what a god complex feels like. Cool.
Starting to feel a bit nutty.
Look, I don't need to be a god here. Let's just win this thing already.
If someone asks me if I'm a god, I'll say yes.
Might need to get myself a new shooting rig if this keeps up.
Watch your step eh? Heaps of danger about.
There's no end to the things I can do to you.
What's this then? Not gonna pay the toll?
Got yourself in a bit of a quandary eh?
Say hello to my little friend!
Could have had you a ways back, but I always pick my spots.
Let me tell you a little story about your gold, and my pocket.
I'm sorry, did you think you were hunting me?
You don't even have anything interesting.
And don't think I'll run out of ammo, I've always got another stash.
You should have stayed out of the woods.
Quit packin' a sad, eh? You lost fair-ish n' square.
I was born for this. You're just a pretender.
Am I this good or is my weapon blessed?
Yeah nah, don't get ahead of yourself.
That one's a bit suss eh? Maybe poke him with a stick.
You're lucky I didn't do worse, but I got time.
You? On a battlefield? Yeah right.
Let's not get too worked up about it.
Don't let it get you down. I'm good. Really, really good
You might take this time to reflect upon why you messed with me in the first place.
You might not think it to look at me, but I've racked up quite the body count.
Try not getting caught with your trousers down.
Do you mind? I'm trying to celebrate.
If I'd known you were a bloody winger, I'd have aimed for the mouth.
Now I should tell you, I don't usually kill my victims straight away.
I could have toyed with you a bit, but you're just not that interesting.
Did you fall out of the nest as a baby?
Any life experience you'd like me to collect on your behalf?
Barked up the wrong tree, I reckon.
Could I kill you just as easy without the crossbow? Of course! But it'd make a helluva mess.
I don't need to gloat. That'd get exhausting.
I got a knack for that.
All's well that ends with me winning.
I got blisters on me fingers.
What else you planning that I can ruin?
Ah ha ha ha ha ha ha ha!
Ha ha ha ha ha ha haa haa!
Eh he he ha ha ha ha!
People say I talk too much.
See keen, shoot keen. It's simple really.
Nothing personal Tinker, I'm just prejudiced.
One keen down, but plenty more to go.
Should I tell you what I got planned for your little contraption?
That's for ruining such a choice word!
Choke on your black powder, scumbags.
If I see one more of you little bastards in my trees, I'll rain down blood on every last one of ya! Dig?
That's what happens when you get a bruiser to fight your battles for you. You get soft.
Don't cry for the likes of her.
I don't know what that horse had against me, but enough is enough.
Hate to shatter your dreams, you frigid idiot.
You eh? To be honest I was hoping for the other one.
The other one might have had better luck.
This one's heaps of fun! Get to kill him again and again!
If I had a gold piece for every Oglodi I kill, I'd have enough to start using acorns for impractical purposes.
I'll never burn that sight outta my brain!
That bat had a giant parasite. I probably did him a favour.
Look, you knew we weren't gonna get along just on general bloody principle.
You're better off drinking maple syrup.
Oh, mate. This one must really sting for you, eh?
I'm getting tipsy just from the stench!
Neath those pickers, you're mince like all the rest.
I reckon this one was worthy of at least a little respect.
If I say what I feel, my tongue might turn black and fall off.
This one feels better than most.
You're lucky we never ran into each other when you were alive. You never would have survived to be cursed!
Yeah you were pretty chill, shame really.
Cheer up eh. Now you can stop whining about your great sacrifice.
Yay for the mischief, but what's with the greed? That's just a waste of your time.
Are they bloody serious with these people? Where does someone like that even come from?
Never had much time for pity parties. Where do you get off?
As you can see, I'm somewhat of a disruptor myself.
All that power... just another case of a stunning lack of imagination.
Wait a second. That dragon could have chosen anyone, and it chose you?! What the hell is wrong with this world.
You obviously weren't born for this. I'm surprised nobody showed you sooner.
Hey, what a coincidence! My first hard targets to practice with were little rolling rocks. I guess they prepared me better than I thought!
It was like aiming at a broadside of an oak. What could be easier?
See the trick is, never set limits for yourself. I never set out to kill a Titan, but I never thought I couldn't neither.
Shooting out candles and torches is easy. But destroying the essence of flame itself? Yeah I'll take it.
You can't tell me what to do! I tell me what to do!
How can someone with no face look so damn smug?
Ha ha look, I gave him a proper face. Let's just call those bloodstains tears.
I'm all out of pity for the likes of you.
Dying light's already a cliché after all.
Yeah, magic's pretty neat and all, but nothing compares to a heavy bolt and a dead shot eye.
Those two dragons crashed together so hard they merged into one dumber slower dragon.
Hoods are way better than masks. Just saying.
Hey old-timer. The sun sets on everybody. Whether they like it or not.
You can think of these trees as masts, if it helps you die in peace.
I'm not joining your bloody legion.
Wait there's one of you here too?!
Bro she is not going to be happy that I killed you. Oh well, she already had it out for me anyway.
You cold dead guys are all the same. Don't you have a convention to be at or something?
Did you see that bloke? There's no way he's not thanking me. And if he's not, he should be.
You singed the fur. There's no coming back from that mate.
Don't mind me. I'm just gonna lop that hand off. I heard I could trade some favors for it in some dumb wizard town.
I'm not here to explain what went wrong. It's just obvious that something did. I mean, otherwise...
I reckon a lot of people felt you had this coming. But that lot's just a bunch of bloody whingers. I did this for fun.
Yeah with how fast you are, you got no one to blame here but yourself. I mean you could have been literally anywhere else.
Spare me your noble sob story. What's it got to do with me?
Okay okay. This is a real feather in my cap. Sure as.
Yeah, dodging snakes is nothing new for me lady. What else you got?
Sorry Meepo. You shouldn't have looked at where I was digging. That was classic misdirection.
Even if the lady hadn't been crazy, I'd have had to kill the cat. Can't have mass murderers running around.
Looks like I'm the king of mischief now.
Aw, mate. That kinda makes me need to go. You know?
Heck, with that singing voice it was either bolt or bolt her. And I felt like staying.
Look, I told you I'm not big on affiliations. Stay outta wherever I am.
Yeah sorry. People with your attitude just rub me the wrong way.
My uncle used to tell me bedtime stories about you. Those were some great adventures. Real happy to have killed you.
Yeah I got a fair bit of luck myself. My uncle used to say I was right blessed. You know, on account of not dying like all my other kin.
Hey just what this place needed, another self-righteous metal marcher on some higher quest.
Wait wait, I want to think of one you never heard before or after.
Yeah, I'm not real keen on what you said about dying in a fire. That's what my crossbow likes to call a trigger warning.
Heard you were some kind of big hullabaloo. I didn't come here to prove anything, but I guess I just did.
Bloody muppet. What were you thinking?
Roll along home you silly bastard.
I can hit anything. Doesn't matter how blurry.
Wouldn't it been better to die all peaceful like, dangling a pole in the river? Not with two bolts in the dome...
When I was just a little bit, I used to wish upon shooting stars. Then I realized that was stupid and just learned to shoot instead.
They used to tell stories about this one in the Tomo'kan. Quite the little troublemaker. This'll gain me even more respect.
Ugh uh, the stench though! How do you get that taste outta your mouth?
You coddled little tail-jerker! Someone shoulda done this ages ago!
Ma'am. This is a forest, not...wherever it is you think you're supposed to be.
Yeah we're light years apart, mate.
Whatever can be made can be unmade, I figure.
Had to leave you cracked and bleeding.
I could smell those fakes a mile away.
That's what you get for hoarding!
I said no snakes of any kind!
Yeah, a lot of people have tried to shut me up. This is how it always plays out.
I don't take kindly to being punched by fish!
I told you to stay off my turf, gill boy.
No one's gonna miss you. Not even you.
On this plane you're just a bobby after all.
Sorry. I didn't feel like staying in today.
Looks like the power grid's out, mate.
My first thought was your sword's impractical. But now I see it's actually impracticable.
Never had much time for book smarts. And this right here's the reason why.
I don't need books to argue a point.
Don't you ever get tired of yourself?
Oh bloody hell. This one's corpse is gonna reek.
I've known some Tinies in my time. You, sir, are no Tiny.
Bummer, I think he had some of my stash. Ah well. I'll find more.
What, did you think I got a problem with snow? I'm right at home.
Wonder if I can turn these horns into some sorta charm.
That's a smell'll strip bark off trees!
Got enough critters in these woods already.
Everyone's got problems, lassie. Yours ain't mine.
Eh, I'd eat slug if times were tight. But they ain't.
Lot harder to fly with all those arrows in you.
Even if I cared for your rules, it's not even close to my time yet.
Guess you shoulda showed up sooner.
So you cut down trees to turn 'em into books about demons? Yeah, you had this coming.
Honestly, I just saw him out of the corner of my eye and started shooting. Was instinct really.
Couldn't take my word for it, could ya?
Yeah, friends is kind of a loose term for me. Sorry.
I don't know if we were enemies, but that poem was depressing as all get out.
Think I'll pass! My uncle went to the doctor once and never came back.
You want these little bones of mine? Gonna have to do better than that!
Since you're not a god anymore, I feel like I can ask you: why are you so messed up?
You think you're special or something?
We coulda been great together. But you always get blinded by the floodlights...
I'm gonna get huge props for this back home.
Yeah if you don't mind I'm gonna help myself to some of your gear.
I don't even know enough about you to care you're dead.
First blood. Well that sets a tone.
First blood! Gotta be quick when I'm around.
First blood! And it's still pulsing.
First blood. And just a crazy amount of it really.
Who said you could stroll in my woods?!
Better not catch you littering, bro.
Anyone seen an ugly little goblin lady riding a big dumb lizard?
Right. See the key to throwing a rider is misdirection. Lemme show you.
I played around with concoctions when I was younger. But now I prefer the natural path.
I'm not keen on frost, yeah? Let's keep it to a minimum.
You do your thing, Anti-Mage. I'll go take care of this lot.
If I had a nut for every bloke who came through these parts with a big head and stories to match...
Yah, I get the loner thing, Axe. Just easier that way, eh?
So like what's your personal favorite nightmare, Bane?
Why you let that fella ride you around then?
Who said you could be on my team Beastmaster? Go on, get out of here.
Yeah, hunting's only really fun if it's not work. So you're doing it wrong, is what I'm saying, Bloodseeker.
I know you think you're collecting contracts, Bounty Hunter, but all I see is selling yourself one piece at a time.
No thanks, Brewmaster. I'm a nasty drunk.
There's a fella can handle his handles.
Who says you need a good reason to fight, Bristleback? Sometimes you just gotta rain hell for the kicks.
None of these ugly mugs are going to keep up with us, Broodmother.
Get that scepter first, Centaur. Then you can join the fun. But lay off the trees eh.
I'm gonna have to rethink some things if you're the god of chaos.
Okay first I'm gonna murder all of them, Chen, and then I'm definitely gonna get back around to you.
There's gotta be an easier way to light your arrows than the whole self-immolation thing...
Look, I can blame whoever I want for whatever I want, Clockwerk. So why don't you just back off?
Hey, another bubbly little killer. This is going to be a great time.
There are plenty of things I hate more than military commanders, Dark Seer. But I still hate them quite a bit.
Hey, Mireska, you ever leave Jex's cage in a tree? Might be we could set up some real neat traps.
I don't understand a word you're saying, Dazzle. But I was barely listening, so's probably ok?
There's a dealth cult that worships in the Tomo'kan. You ever been there Death Prophet?
Which one of you's the smart one?
We all got issues, Doom. Deal with 'em. In a way that's better than this.
Why are all you dragon kind so stingy with the piggy backs eh?
Look, social skills are like any other, Traxex. You gotta miss a few shots before you start hitting the mark.
I nicked a statue that looked kinda like you once. Yeah, threw it by the side of the road. Wonder if somebody grabbed it.
Which direction is Nishai from here anyway?
You made a world, yeah? How about making me some new bolts?
On behalf of my tail, I'd kindly ask you to keep about ten paces off at all times. Killer.
What'd you bring me, Auntie A? Something good?
Yeah, I'm good, Auntie. Feeling strong and my rig here's doing all right.
Hey, Faceless Void. What do those glyphs mean? I saw a bunch just like em on some broken archway I found in a cave.
Yeah nah, I think you actually wished people liked you, Grimstroke. This loner thing's all just an act.
I haven't decided on you yet, Gyrocopter. But I'm leaning towards dislike.
Who teaches these maniacs how to make fire?
Know where I've always wanted to go, Io? Hah, what am I saying. Of course you do!
Did you have anything to do with the curses of the Tomo'kan?
I dunno how you do it. That level of cooperation's beyond me.
Hey, give us your mask for sec?
I kind of wanted to sleep in today, gramps.
I'm not real interested in sea legs. Tree legs is more my style.
Oh you're gonna make things easy for me today, Tresdin.
Get back to me when you learn something 'telligible.
Long as you're carefull, I think we're gonna get on like gangbusters.
Not real interested in your life philosophy, Lion.
Oh, what a cutie. I wouldn't even guess he's not real.
Keep the saliva in your mouth, Nova. Or I'll pin it shut.
You stop having fun just to join some cult?
I've run across some shapeshifters in the dark wood. They move around a lot, but I can tell you about where.
I'll get an acorn ready, Magnus. This is gonna be bloody epic.
That song's really catchy, Mars. Too bad you're tonedeaf.
So...do the snakes get hungry? Asking for a friend...
Hey Meepo, got that special varnish I ordered? 'Member? I paid you up front.
Still slummin' in that temple life, Mirana?
I see you eyin' me, Sagan. Not bloody likely.
I heard you came to my neck of the woods once, Wu Kong. But it was before I was born.
Yeah, but like, in a pinch could someone drink ya?
Sweet as! Let me grab my togs.
So were you like really weirded out the first time you heard your voice on dry land?
You always think you know best, Prophet. I don't care who sprout you, no one bosses me around in my woods.
So do you miss thinking for yourself? Guess not, else you'd still be doing it.
I'm not interested in my future. Now's all I need.
I'm all in for your shenanigans, Donté.
How do they grow 'em so big in your place?
Someone's been looking for you, Puck. I got a message.
So is that how people dress where you're from or are you making a statement?
Want me to give you some tips on how I roll?
Just gonna tell you now: nothing shuts me up.
Wings up, chooka boy. Time to stop moping about.
Do you even know what you did to me, Snapfire? To everyone?!
I don't blame you, Mortimer. But your saddle partner's gotta die.
Stay away from me with that stink wagon.
You don't seem to be friends with that wretched lady, Kardel. Maybe you're all right...
How do I hitch a lift?
Why's all my hair standing on end?
That sword's bigger'n you are. Pretty neat!
I'm gonna have to learn to compartmentalize if I wanna get through this.
Your stuff's worse than powder. Remind me to show you something after the fight.
Is it time, Tiny? Is it time?
Hey can I check out your upper branches? It'll only take a sec.
Your style is right by me, Troll. I think everyone but me is an idiot, too.
I need to suss out some peppermint or something.
Vengeance can be bloody good fun, lady. I think you're missing most of the point.
Can you magic me up a portal into Krimwohl big enough for a Durana swarm?
There's heaps of musty old spellbooks scattered around the Tomo'kan. Most of 'em are half rotten. But you might find something stupid enough to catch your eye.
I don't think we've got much in common, Weaver. But have a nice one.
Nothing like a choice bit of green, eh Windranger?
I bet I get twice as many notches as you, Lyralei.
I'm just saying, a squirrel riding a dragon into battle would be pretty damn epic.
I grok'd smoking was bad for you, Ostarion, but this is bloody nuts!
I don't care what you can turn into. The answer's always gonna be no.
Where do you find the time for all this?
I know I'm a born star, but the answer's still no.
Nah yeah...thought I might be seeing you when I noticed your leash was nicked. No hard feelings?
We used to be friends, a long time ago. What say we give it another run?
I couldn't have known everything'd go nuts up like that. Honest!
What's the good word from the Crow's Nest?
Good as gold. Worthless, useless gold.
Oh yay, gold. Like I haven't seen that before.
Any of you creeps got something better?
I could go for a bit of brekkie.
How many of these creeps are there?
That's gotta be the last one.
Like I haven't seen that before.
I just like taking what's yours.
Don't I have better things to do?
No, see? This is my sorry face.
Just teachin' ya a lesson for next time.
And you were looking proper stoked too...
No need to get snooty over it.
You were just, like a second too slow.
I make a very fine point.
Don't bust a gut on me.
I thought we talked about this.
You look a bit crook, mate.
The crank does most of the work!
I never said he was my friend.
He won't hold it against me.
Don't know why you'd want any of this dumb gold, but I'll definitely take your wares.
Aren't you getting a bit ripped off?
And you thought I was hard to keep track before.
What's this? Some sort of big deal or something?
Oh wow, that feels nice. Wanna kill something?
You take this off that Aghanim fella yourself?
All new meaning to the term critter!
You've ever look through one of these?
I don't normally go for footwear, but these are kind of nice.
I'm the strongest critter that ever lived!
I didn't think this would fit.
I'll take it over faith any day.
This cost how much?! I'm in the wrong business.
This side goes towards the enemy.
Ehhh... That's not good as a hood.
How'd I get swindled into paying for this?
I'm just throwing money away at this point.
There's always something funny about a good zap.
I'll try not to cut myself.
It's like it was made for me.
Sure, I sing sometimes. But only by myself.
I prefer a waterskin, but magic's magic.
Hey, hey. Anyone else feeling like really, really ready right now?
Sorry everybody, trouble just found you.
They could barely see me as it is.
I always do stir up a storm.
Yea, sure, a Magic Stick, you're lucky I like sticks.
They give out medallions for that now?
How am I even lifting it?
Does that Monkey guy know you nicked his stuff?
Honestly, this is about all I need to get started.
Solving the world's problems one sesh at a time.
I like to swap on the fly!
I love it when they stand real still, just whimpering and begging for their miserable lives. What now?
Guess I could bulk up a bit.
This'll suss out any sneaky little scumbags.
Sweet as, I should get heaps of these.
What a lovely pair. Or I guess together we're a trio.
Oh those.. are kind of comfy.
Wait, if the Gleipnir's here. Then he's... I gotta go.
Jeez, this thing was impossible to make, how did you get your hands on it?
You really should've left this thing where it was, for all our sakes.
Aw mate, do you know how hard I had to work to get that thing the first time I needed it?
Okay, lets see if I can murder all of you before I lose the first one.
You'd be lucky if I only lived twice.
Ever seen a body with nothing left to lose?
Watch the tail, eh. That's genuine fur.
I beat the odds, lasting this long...
That's what I get for being distracted...
Toss that one in the dunny...
Of course I underestimated you. Look at you!
Have you ever seen...a more beautiful corpse?
Before I die...I just need you to know...you suck.
Right. Plan B it is. Hunt down their families.
One good cock up deserves another.
The last laugh? They can have it. I'm not gonna be laughing after what I do to 'em. That's just sick.
We'll see who's carked it next time. And it'll be you. It'll be the whole bloody lot of you!
What on earth was that all about?
Some people take things way too personally.
